    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The perceived result of rays of light turned back when they strike a surface and are not absorbed, as from a mirror.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
